snippet.title: Johnny Depp Testifies That Marriage to Amber Heard was "Crime Scene Waiting to Happen"
snippet.description:
#JohnnyDepp in a British courtroom launching a libel suit against the tabloid #TheSUN. The Hollywood titan testified that the marriage to his ex-wife #AmberHeard was a "crime scene waiting to happen."
